CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

April 27, 2010

[Cite as 04/27/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-1812.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2010-0662. State v. Duncan.

Richland App. No. 2009CA028, 2009-Ohio-5668. This cause is pending before the court as a claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.

Pfeifer, Acting C.J. The late Chief Justice Thomas J. Moyer did not participate in the ruling in this case.
